and silenced the killer.

293
00:13:44,919 --> 00:13:45,639
That is why

294
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:47,440
this thumb ring

295
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:49,240
ended up on Cai.

296
00:13:50,279 --> 00:13:51,120
Master,

297
00:13:51,399 --> 00:13:52,200
I am right, am I not?

298
00:13:57,320 --> 00:13:59,679
Where is the witness
who saw Wang Xian kill Cai?

299
00:14:01,840 --> 00:14:02,240
Well...

300
00:14:02,919 --> 00:14:05,360
What you said does sound reasonable.

301
00:14:05,799 --> 00:14:07,840
But Laifu can only prove

302
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:08,960
that Wang Xian hired killers.

303
00:14:09,240 --> 00:14:10,919
Even if we confirm

304
00:14:10,919 --> 00:14:13,000
that Cai met Wang Xian afterward,

305
00:14:13,519 --> 00:14:15,039
this thumb ring alone

306
00:14:15,039 --> 00:14:16,759
is not enough to convict Wang Xian.

307
00:14:17,639 --> 00:14:18,919
We still need a witness.

308
00:14:19,480 --> 00:14:20,200
Official Di,

309
00:14:20,519 --> 00:14:22,559
I actually think Lin Buyan has a point.

310
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:25,120
If Wang Xian did not kill anyone,

311
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:27,240
then why did Wang Dingrong
send people to kill Laifu?

312
00:14:27,559 --> 00:14:28,559
Exactly, Master.

313
00:14:28,559 --> 00:14:30,240
Wang Dingrong's men already confessed.

314
00:14:30,600 --> 00:14:32,320
It is a fact that Wang Dingrong
wanted Laifu dead.

315
00:14:32,320 --> 00:14:33,360
Wasn't he trying to kill Laifu

316
00:14:33,399 --> 00:14:34,440
to help his son

317
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:35,799
cover up the truth?

318
00:14:35,799 --> 00:14:36,559
If you ask me,

319
00:14:36,559 --> 00:14:38,480
he definitely knows
where Wang Xian is hiding.

320
00:14:38,559 --> 00:14:40,240
Bring him in for questioning
and the truth will come out.

321
00:14:40,799 --> 00:14:41,639
Do not act rashly.

322
00:14:42,399 --> 00:14:44,360
Even if your reasoning is correct,

323
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:46,440
once we arrest Wang Dingrong,

324
00:14:46,799 --> 00:14:48,639
will Wang Xian still return?

325
00:14:50,399 --> 00:14:52,080
Do not alert the enemy.

326
00:14:52,679 --> 00:14:53,519
Tell the public

327
00:14:53,759 --> 00:14:56,519
that we are still searching for Laifu.

328
00:14:58,980 --> 00:15:01,660
(Fortune Telling. Divination)

329
00:15:06,720 --> 00:15:09,879
It hurts.

330
00:15:09,879 --> 00:15:12,159
It's killing me.

331
00:15:12,159 --> 00:15:12,799
Master Diviner.

332
00:15:12,840 --> 00:15:13,639
(Medical Shop)
It's killing me.

333
00:15:13,639 --> 00:15:14,480
What ails you, Master?

334
00:15:14,480 --> 00:15:17,320
It feels like my bone is about to break.

335
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:18,440
Don't worry.

336
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:19,120
Let me take a look.

337
00:15:19,279 --> 00:15:20,120
Let me take a look.

338
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:22,879
Not this leg.

339
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:31,679
Master,

340
00:15:32,320 --> 00:15:33,440
there is nothing wrong

341
00:15:33,720 --> 00:15:35,159
with your leg.

342
00:15:37,639 --> 00:15:38,480
Nothing wrong?

343
00:15:39,279 --> 00:15:40,840
Maybe you simply can't tell.

344
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:42,440
Could you be a quack?

345
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:45,679
I can tell with one touch
whether your leg is injured.

346
00:15:46,039 --> 00:15:48,320
If even I can't find anything wrong,

347
00:15:48,320 --> 00:15:49,799
no doctor anywhere

348
00:15:50,240 --> 00:15:51,320
will find anything wrong either.

349
00:15:51,879 --> 00:15:53,279
That can't be right.

350
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:55,240
Divine Doctor.

351
00:15:55,279 --> 00:15:56,879
I heard your greatest skill

352
00:15:56,919 --> 00:15:58,559
is finding illness where there is none.

353
00:15:58,559 --> 00:15:59,440
If you say

354
00:15:59,480 --> 00:16:01,120
his leg was broken,

355
00:16:01,120 --> 00:16:03,039
he'd probably believe it himself.

356
00:16:03,080 --> 00:16:04,440
Am I wrong?

357
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:07,519
If your leg is injured,

358
00:16:07,519 --> 00:16:10,000
I guarantee I can cure it.

359
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:13,000
But if the problem lies elsewhere,

360
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:15,200
turn right when you leave

361
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:16,879
and get yourself a few herbal remedies.

362
00:16:16,879 --> 00:16:18,679
You might still be saved.

363
00:16:19,320 --> 00:16:20,679
Divine Doctor, don't be angry.

364
00:16:20,720 --> 00:16:22,840
I was only joking with you.

365
00:16:24,960 --> 00:16:28,559
I saw a sinister aura

366
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:31,840
hanging over your clinic,

367
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:34,960
so I came specially to warn you.

368
00:16:38,360 --> 00:16:40,000
I won't claim

369
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:41,639
I've never lost a patient,

370
00:16:41,759 --> 00:16:43,360
but my conscience is clear.

371
00:16:43,360 --> 00:16:45,639
Why would I fear some evil aura?

372
00:16:45,679 --> 00:16:46,360
No!

373
00:16:46,639 --> 00:16:48,039
What truly worries me
is someone like you,

374
00:16:48,120 --> 00:16:49,120
who unknowingly

375
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:51,120
helps evil thrive.

376
00:16:51,759 --> 00:16:53,320
This sinister aura

377
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:55,799
has lingered here for two years.

378
00:16:55,799 --> 00:16:57,679
I fear your household
has known no peace,

379
00:16:57,720 --> 00:16:58,679
and the resentment has only deepened.

380
00:16:58,679 --> 00:17:00,039
This will be difficult.

381
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:00,679
Forget it.

382
00:17:00,759 --> 00:17:02,559
Since you are unwilling,

383
00:17:02,559 --> 00:17:03,840
then we

384
00:17:03,840 --> 00:17:04,920
were never meant

385
00:17:04,920 --> 00:17:06,440
to cross paths.

386
00:17:06,440 --> 00:17:07,440
Master Diviner.

387
00:17:07,759 --> 00:17:09,119
Please wait.

388
00:17:10,079 --> 00:17:11,039
You said

389
00:17:11,440 --> 00:17:13,680
this sinister aura
has lingered for two years.

390
00:17:13,920 --> 00:17:15,599
That suddenly reminded me.

391
00:17:15,599 --> 00:17:18,559
Two years ago,
my son developed an eye disease.

392
00:17:18,799 --> 00:17:21,359
Though people call me a Divine Doctor,

393
00:17:21,720 --> 00:17:23,279
I simply could not cure him.

394
00:17:23,519 --> 00:17:26,119
When you spoke
of unrest in my household,

395
00:17:27,160 --> 00:17:28,119
were you

396
00:17:28,559 --> 00:17:29,759
referring to this?

397
00:17:30,559 --> 00:17:31,559
Yes.

398
00:17:31,559 --> 00:17:33,160
Exactly.

399
00:17:33,160 --> 00:17:34,359
If this drags on any longer,

400
00:17:34,400 --> 00:17:35,880
it will not just be an eye disease.

401
00:17:36,240 --> 00:17:37,359
Then how do I resolve it?

402
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:41,359
Everything happens for a reason.

403
00:17:43,359 --> 00:17:45,720
Why do you think I came here
pretending this leg was injured?

404
00:17:45,759 --> 00:17:48,519
Naturally, because I divined something.

405
00:17:48,599 --> 00:17:49,480
Think carefully.

406
00:17:49,559 --> 00:17:50,119
Two years ago,

407
00:17:50,119 --> 00:17:51,640
did you do something
against your conscience

408
00:17:51,640 --> 00:17:53,599
that led to someone's death?

409
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:56,079
The leg...

410
00:17:57,359 --> 00:17:58,559
Two years ago...

411
00:17:59,640 --> 00:18:01,359
No one truly died

412
00:18:02,839 --> 00:18:04,319
because of this.

413
00:18:04,359 --> 00:18:06,200
That is strange.

414
00:18:06,240 --> 00:18:08,759
Let me ask this sinister aura.

415
00:18:08,799 --> 00:18:09,759
Move aside.

416
00:18:21,359 --> 00:18:22,839
Leave for now.

417
00:18:22,839 --> 00:18:25,279
I will seek justice for you.

418
00:18:29,160 --> 00:18:30,640
Are you

419
00:18:30,640 --> 00:18:33,000
a diviner or a shaman?

420
00:18:36,960 --> 00:18:37,960
People in our line of work

421
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:39,880
need to know a bit of everything.

422
00:18:44,839 --> 00:18:45,759
In that direction ahead,

423
00:18:45,799 --> 00:18:47,640
did anyone come here for treatment
two years ago?

424
00:18:50,039 --> 00:18:50,559
The Wang...

425
00:18:50,759 --> 00:18:51,599
The Wang family.

426
00:18:52,960 --> 00:18:55,079
This clinic sits near
the Ruanjiang waters.

427
00:18:55,079 --> 00:18:57,079
The water ghost
has been causing trouble lately.

428
00:18:57,119 --> 00:18:58,480
The water ghost takes lives.

429
00:18:58,480 --> 00:19:00,079
You'd best be careful.

430
00:19:00,119 --> 00:19:01,000
Of course,

431
00:19:01,039 --> 00:19:03,519
an upright man fears no shadow.

432
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:06,240
Impossible.

433
00:19:06,759 --> 00:19:09,519
Master Wang's leg
truly was broken back then.

434
00:19:10,279 --> 00:19:11,880
But that had nothing

435
00:19:11,880 --> 00:19:13,079
to do with me.

436
00:19:13,519 --> 00:19:15,599
I heard about it too.

437
00:19:15,799 --> 00:19:17,079
But now that you mention it,
it is rather strange.

438
00:19:17,079 --> 00:19:18,920
Why did his leg break

439
00:19:18,960 --> 00:19:20,279
on that exact day?

440
00:19:20,279 --> 00:19:21,839
And why did something happen

441
00:19:21,880 --> 00:19:23,400
to the ship on that same day?

442
00:19:24,160 --> 00:19:26,279
Is there anything else

443
00:19:26,279 --> 00:19:27,240
you find strange enough to tell me?

444
00:19:28,039 --> 00:19:29,039
And...

445
00:19:29,039 --> 00:19:30,039
What?

446
00:19:31,119 --> 00:19:32,640
I...

447
00:19:33,640 --> 00:19:36,000
You have to say it
before I can help you.

448
00:19:40,079 --> 00:19:41,519
Master Wang's leg

449
00:19:41,519 --> 00:19:42,519
was broken

450
00:19:42,519 --> 00:19:43,519
by someone else.

451
00:19:51,060 --> 00:19:52,220
(Preview of Next Episode)

452
00:19:55,559 --> 00:19:57,240
This used to be where you secretly met.

453
00:19:57,759 --> 00:19:59,559
Now it belongs to us.

454
00:20:07,440 --> 00:20:08,759
(You did this)

455
00:20:08,759 --> 00:20:10,759
(to make it look certain
that Wang Xian killed to silence someone.)

456
00:20:11,160 --> 00:20:13,559
(You must hate Wang Xian to the core.)

457
00:20:14,400 --> 00:20:16,480
(Who exactly are you?)

458
00:20:23,710 --> 00:20:25,290
♪Night covers the long streets♪

459
00:20:26,370 --> 00:20:28,080
♪The city remains silent♪

460
00:20:29,470 --> 00:20:31,060
♪Wind turns the old pages♪

461
00:20:31,320 --> 00:20:33,560
♪Words still left unspoken♪

462
00:20:34,960 --> 00:20:36,600
♪Bloodstains still hold their warmth♪

463
00:20:37,730 --> 00:20:40,200
♪Lamplight slowly tilts aside♪

464
00:20:40,820 --> 00:20:42,300
♪Who hides in the shadows♪

465
00:20:42,300 --> 00:20:45,440
♪Still circling around the truth?♪

466
00:20:46,060 --> 00:20:47,980
♪Love is born from desire♪

467
00:20:48,670 --> 00:20:50,800
♪Hatred rises out of greed♪

468
00:20:51,940 --> 00:20:53,600
♪One thought becomes a snare♪

469
00:20:53,600 --> 00:20:56,900
♪A lifetime trapped within♪

470
00:20:58,350 --> 00:20:59,670
♪Someone once warned me♪

471
00:20:59,670 --> 00:21:01,190
♪To stop upon this shore♪

472
00:21:01,190 --> 00:21:02,510
♪But sunlight burns too fiercely♪

473
00:21:02,510 --> 00:21:04,000
♪Fragile eyes break too easily♪

474
00:21:04,000 --> 00:21:05,120
♪If one thought retreats♪

475
00:21:05,120 --> 00:21:06,420
♪Then all things rest in peace♪

476
00:21:06,420 --> 00:21:07,760
♪But in this world♪

477
00:21:07,760 --> 00:21:10,160
♪Who will make the final judgment?♪

478
00:21:11,990 --> 00:21:14,800
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

479
00:21:14,800 --> 00:21:16,270
♪Still I walk ahead♪

480
00:21:16,500 --> 00:21:17,720
♪Let it pierce through♪

481
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:22,460
♪The illusions before my eyes♪

482
00:21:22,460 --> 00:21:24,700
♪Layer upon layer of deception♪

483
00:21:24,700 --> 00:21:26,100
♪Covering every heart♪

484
00:21:26,100 --> 00:21:27,290
♪How many people♪

485
00:21:27,550 --> 00:21:28,920
♪Weave their own cocoon♪

486
00:21:28,920 --> 00:21:31,130
♪Yet call it♪

487
00:21:31,330 --> 00:21:32,670
♪Fate?♪

488
00:21:33,030 --> 00:21:34,210
♪Life and death♪

489
00:21:34,210 --> 00:21:35,470
♪Balanced on a single line♪

490
00:21:35,820 --> 00:21:36,990
♪Light and shadow♪

491
00:21:36,990 --> 00:21:38,250
♪Hanging side by side♪

492
00:21:38,250 --> 00:21:39,730
♪Goodness is not absolute♪

493
00:21:39,730 --> 00:21:41,140
♪Nor is evil ever complete♪

494
00:21:41,140 --> 00:21:42,680
♪In the end, it is only♪

495
00:21:42,680 --> 00:21:44,060
♪A single misguided thought♪

496
00:21:44,060 --> 00:21:45,620
♪If unveiling the truth♪

497
00:21:45,620 --> 00:21:46,960
♪Requires abandoning tenderness♪

498
00:21:46,960 --> 00:21:48,130
♪Then this answer♪

499
00:21:48,130 --> 00:21:49,490
♪Can it still remain true?♪

500
00:21:49,490 --> 00:21:50,890
♪When love and law♪

501
00:21:50,890 --> 00:21:52,370
♪Stand against each other in silence♪

502
00:21:52,370 --> 00:21:53,770
♪Which figure before me♪

503
00:21:53,770 --> 00:22:00,970
♪Am I meant to believe?♪

504
00:22:00,970 --> 00:22:03,700
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

505
00:22:03,700 --> 00:22:05,290
♪Still I walk ahead♪

506
00:22:05,290 --> 00:22:06,530
♪Not for fame or glory♪

507
00:22:06,530 --> 00:22:11,400
♪Nor caring who wins or loses♪

508
00:22:11,400 --> 00:22:13,210
♪Human nature is clouded♪

509
00:22:13,210 --> 00:22:14,930
♪Yet still reflects the stars♪

510
00:22:14,930 --> 00:22:16,400
♪Though this world♪

511
00:22:16,400 --> 00:22:17,770
♪Is filled with mud and mire♪

512
00:22:17,770 --> 00:22:20,020
♪There is still a light♪

513
00:22:20,020 --> 00:22:22,980
♪Worth pursuing♪

514
00:22:22,980 --> 00:22:24,800
♪Every case has its ending♪

515
00:22:24,800 --> 00:22:26,060
♪But night does not always fade♪

516
00:22:26,330 --> 00:22:27,710
♪The wind stops, the pages close♪

517
00:22:27,710 --> 00:22:28,930
♪Yet hearts remain unsettled♪

518
00:22:29,200 --> 00:22:30,280
♪If justice stands♪

519
00:22:30,280 --> 00:22:31,530
♪Without mercy beside it♪

520
00:22:31,530 --> 00:22:33,330
♪Then how is it♪

521
00:22:33,330 --> 00:22:42,890
♪Any different from a blade?♪

522
00:22:42,890 --> 00:22:46,080
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

523
00:22:46,080 --> 00:22:47,560
♪Still I walk ahead♪

524
00:22:47,560 --> 00:22:48,950
♪Even if the world♪

525
00:22:48,950 --> 00:22:53,680
♪Refuses to answer♪

526
00:22:53,680 --> 00:22:55,640
♪When every hidden truth♪

527
00:22:55,640 --> 00:22:57,350
♪Finally reveals itself♪

528
00:22:57,350 --> 00:22:58,710
♪I only wish♪

529
00:22:58,710 --> 00:23:00,190
♪To hold on♪

530
00:23:00,190 --> 00:23:04,930
♪Within the darkness♪

531
00:23:04,930 --> 00:23:06,930
♪To the heart♪

